cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SD 

The paper deals with analyzing images of clouds, which is a task that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of ground-based sky cameras and satellite images also involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the correlation between different types of cloud cover data, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and statistical analysis (cs.SD).
